    ('4f60d12f-6805-484d-9d84-bb6301653ed9', 'a6b5aa0f-d9dd-42b2-818f-e29977169dfd', 'Sugar Pie', 'Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (175 degrees C). Grease a 9-inch pie dish.
